# ⭐ Exam / Interview Questions

### Q1. CPU ka function?

**Ans:** Instructions execute karta hai aur processing karta hai.

### Q2. RAM volatile kyun kehlati hai?

**Ans:** Power off hote hi data erase ho jata hai.

### Q3. SSD aur HDD ka purpose?

**Ans:** Permanent data storage.

### Q4. POST ka full form?

**Ans:** Power-On Self Test.

### Q5. BIOS/UEFI ka kaam?

**Ans:** Hardware initialize karna aur Operating System boot karna.

### Q6. Motherboard ka role?

**Ans:** Sabhi hardware components ko connect aur communicate karwana.

